ashion faces Rs 217 lakh demand from customs over IGST dispute.\nThe company plans to legally contest the demand order at CESTAT.","summary":"Aditya Birla Fashion faces Rs 217 lakh demand from customs over IGST dispute.\nThe company plans to legally contest the demand order at CESTAT.","url":"https://sqst.in/Z0jBk","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-01-21T15:11:23","source":"ScoutQuest"},{"id":"801298019446657664","title":"Aditya Birla Fashion shares fell 8% after equity deals worth ₹289 crore.","summary":"Aditya Birla Fashion shares fell 8% after equity deals worth ₹289 crore.","url":"https://sqst.in/shareMessage?msgId=801298019446657633","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-01-20T09:22:15","source":"ScoutQuest"},{"id":"445625","title":"Aditya Birla Fashion plans to sell 3% stake via block deal worth $32M.\nThe deal starts at ₹65.78/share, 8.5% below current market price.","summary":"Aditya Birla Fashion plans to sell 3% stake via block deal worth $32M.\nThe deal starts at ₹65.78/share, 8.5% below current market price.","url":"","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-01-19T20:29:02","source":"Livesquawk"},{"id":"796978878741266176","title":"Aditya Birla Fashion & Retail's Q3 retail segment grew 46% YoY; consolidated revenue rose 35.6%.\neCommerce operations increased 138% YoY, contributing 5.1% of total revenue.","summary":"Aditya Birla Fashion & Retail's Q3 retail segment grew 46% YoY; consolidated revenue rose 35.6%.\neCommerce operations increased 138% YoY, contributing 5.1% of total revenue.","url":"https://sqst.in/shareMessage?msgId=796978878741266199","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-01-08T11:19:31","source":"ScoutQuest"},{"id":"794186394948032512","title":"Aditya Birla Fashion faces a tax demand of ₹132.9 crore from Haryana tax authority.\nThe company denies charges, plans to appeal against the demand order.","summary":"Aditya Birla Fashion faces a tax demand of ₹132.9 crore from Haryana tax authority.\nThe company denies charges, plans to appeal against the demand order.",